<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <link rel="icon" href="/images/favicon.png" type="image/x-icon">
    <link rel="icon" href="/images/favicon.png" type="image/png">
    <link rel="shortcut icon" href="/images/favicon.png" type="image/x-icon">
    <title>Claudia & Nahum</title>
    <style>
        @font-face {
            font-family: titlesWedding;
            src: url(../fonts/Vogue.ttf);

        }
        @font-face {
            font-family: cinzel;
            src: url(../fonts/Cinzel.ttf);

        }
        @font-face {
            font-family: Outfit;
            src: url(../fonts/Outfit.ttf);
        }
        @font-face {
            font-family: Raleway;
            src: url(../fonts/Raleway.ttf);
        }
        @font-face {
            font-family: Autography;
            src: url(../fonts/Autography.otf);
        }
        @font-face {
            font-family: Signature;
            src: url(../fonts/Signature.ttf);
        }
        @font-face {
            font-family: Vogue;
            src: url(../fonts/Vogue.ttf);
        }
        *{
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            box-sizing: border-box;
        }
        html{
            font-size: 10px;
        }
        .main_container{
            width: 100vw;
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: column;
            justify-content: center;
            align-items: center;
            height: 100vh;
            background-image: url("/images/NahunClau_Preboda-43.webp");
            background-size: cover;
            background-repeat: no-repeat;


        }

        .main_container::after{
            content: '';
            position: absolute;
            top: 0;
            left: 0;
            width: 100%;
            height: 100%;
            background-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.5);
        }

        h1{
            z-index: 1000;
            font-size: 20rem;
            color: white;
            font-family: titlesWedding, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, 'Segoe UI', Roboto, Oxygen, Ubuntu, Cantarell, 'Open Sans', 'Helvetica Neue', sans-serif;
        }
        h2{
            z-index: 1000;
            font-size: 3.8rem;
            color: white;
            font-family: Outfit, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, 'Segoe UI', Roboto, Oxygen, Ubuntu, Cantarell, 'Open Sans', 'Helvetica Neue', sans-serif;
        }
        p{
            z-index: 1000;
            font-size: 2.4rem;
            color: white;
            text-align: center;
            margin: 20px 0;
            font-family: Outfit, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, 'Segoe UI', Roboto, Oxygen, Ubuntu, Cantarell, 'Open Sans', 'Helvetica Neue', sans-serif;
        }
        a{
            z-index: 1000;
            font-size: 1.8rem;
            color: white;
            text-decoration: none;
            background-color: #c0a080;
            padding: 10px 20px;
            border-radius: 5px;
            transition: 0.3s;
            font-family: Outfit, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, 'Segoe UI', Roboto, Oxygen, Ubuntu, Cantarell, 'Open Sans', 'Helvetica Neue', sans-serif;
        }
        a:hover{
            background-color: #895d30;
        }

        @media screen and (max-width: 768px){
            .main_container{
                background-image: url("/images/NahunClau_Preboda-15.jpg");
                background-position: center;
            }
            h1{
                font-size: 15rem;
            
            }
            h2{
                font-size: 2.8rem;
            }
            p{
                font-size: 2rem;
                width: 70%;
            }
            a{
                font-size: 1.6rem;
            }

        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    
    <div class="main_container">
        <h1>404</h1>
        <h2>Página no encontrada</h2>
        <p>Lo sentimos, la página que buscas no existe</p>
        <a href="/">Ir al inicio</a>
    </div>


</body>
</html>